divs: Sighting DetailsWas taking pictures of the sunset while on an Alaska Cruise. Didn't see the object when taking the photo, although, I did have a feeling as though something would appear on the photo. Upon my return home, was sifting through the photos on my camera, and the object caught my eye. Is this a ufo? Note: Time on Camera shows 10:40 PST (California). Alaska is 1hr behind 9:40pm.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Between Skagway and Ketch
